cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this methodology or build on this work, please cite the paper."
type: software
title: "ensemble-divergence"
abstract: >
  Structural opacity scoring and ensemble divergence methodology for AI systems
  auditing. Identifies implicit contracts — undeclared preconditions, orphaned
  invariants, and composition seams — in source code and research methods
  descriptions by running multiple independent models against the same artifact
  and treating disagreement as a structural signal.
authors:
